{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Julie, you wouldn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was telling you about the Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I used to walk the other way to cross to get past the thoroughfares.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether you have seen at the Holocaust Museum the big bridge in the Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to walk along the barbed wire fence for about 10 blocks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very dangerous on the street because you never knew who might want to just take a potshot shot at you and kill you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Up those stairs in 20, 30 degrees below, slip and slide, cross over to the other side, walk along the fence again till I got to a distribution center, pick up a sack of, I don't know, probably 30, 40 pounds of potatoes, sling it on my back, take it home.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, this might have to last us three to six months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The thing that I remember the most about the large ghetto are death wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were a daily routine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And now you get used to anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Usually pulled by human beings, men, two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How they knew where the bodies were, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a girlfriend who died of tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She looked so healthy when I met her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't believe we-- we weren't used to pink cheeks in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We all looked like skeletons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she had the brightest red cheeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one day she started coughing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I took a look at her, and it was pink foam, and then it turned to blood just pouring, trickling down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Within about three, four months she died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The TB had spread to her bones, to every organ.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "See, we had doctors, but we had no medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
